Can you tell us a
little bit about how

00:27:58.790 --> 00:28:01.730
you think the has team has
fared versus those expectations?

00:28:01.730 --> 00:28:05.800
And maybe anything that
needs to change for the team,

00:28:05.800 --> 00:28:07.510
moving forward?

00:28:07.510 --> 00:28:11.620
PATRICK VIEIRA: There's
