00:29:51.580 --> 00:29:54.700
is, say, versus the
European leagues

00:29:54.700 --> 00:29:56.210
where you played in the past?

00:29:56.210 --> 00:29:58.585
PATRICK VIEIRA: I think is
really different because we're

00:29:58.585 --> 00:30:02.270
talking about the MLS who had
only 20 years of existence.

00:30:02.270 --> 00:30:04.740
