00:33:12.474 --> 00:33:14.014
PATRICK VIEIRA: It
is a long way off.

00:33:14.014 --> 00:33:16.270
JON JAKLITSCH: It's a
long ways off for us here.

00:33:16.270 --> 00:33:18.880
Do you think it'll take
that long for the MLS,

00:33:18.880 --> 00:33:22.130
