If they do well and if
they have one player who

00:34:39.030 --> 00:34:44.100
can be an example or a role
model for the young players,

00:34:44.100 --> 00:34:45.315
that would be even better.

00:34:45.315 --> 00:34:47.440
JON JAKLITSCH: What do
