00:34:50.260 --> 00:34:52.489
Cup-- as the US making it
out of the group of death,

00:34:52.489 --> 00:34:54.440
making it to the round of 16.

00:34:54.440 --> 00:34:56.489
Do you think winning the finals?

00:34:56.489 --> 00:34:57.406
What do you classify--

00:34:57.406 --> 00:34:58.738
PATRICK VIEIRA: You have to win.

00:34:58.738 --> 00:35:00.190
JON JAKLITSCH: You have to win.

00:35:00.190 --> 00:35:03.407
This is a tough guy over here.

00:35:03.407 --> 00:35:04.740
PATRICK VIEIRA: You have to win.

00:35:04.740 --> 00:35:08.170
 

00:35:08.170 --> 00:35:11.370
This is the society
where we are living.

00:35:11.370 --> 00:35:14.150
You need to win.

00:35:14.150 --> 00:35:18.770
You need to win, you need
to have a role model,

00:35:18.770 --> 00:35:21.460
like basketball.

00:35:21.460 --> 00:35:25.310
Basketball carries one of the
best players at the moment

00:35:25.310 --> 00:35:27.920
and he's an example
for the young players.

00:35:27.920 --> 00:35:29.870
And they always need
this kind of person

00:35:29.870 --> 00:35:33.050
that can lead the sport.

00:35:33.050 --> 00:35:37.650
And this is what they don't
even find yet in football.

00:35:37.650 --> 00:35:40.510
If they find that person
who can be the role model

00:35:40.510 --> 00:35:43.590
and be one of the best
players in the world,

00:35:43.590 --> 00:35:45.386
then you will have
more young players

00:35:45.386 --> 00:35:46.760
who will play
soccer because they

00:35:46.760 --> 00:35:48.467
