00:36:00.240 --> 00:36:05.690
In France, we always managed
to have one player who

00:36:05.690 --> 00:36:10.220
is part of the best
players in the world

00:36:10.220 --> 00:36:12.570
and he was a good role
model for the young players.

00:36:12.570 --> 00:36:14.070
And I think, in
the US, if you have

00:36:14.070 --> 00:36:17.819
that, that will help to develop
the game in the country.

00:36:17.819 --> 00:36:19.694
JON JAKLITSCH: Hopefully,
that's sooner than

00:36:19.694 --> 00:36:21.659
20 to 30 years, but we'll see.

