00:48:33.370 --> 00:48:39.097
Is that the same talent there?

00:48:39.097 --> 00:48:40.430
PATRICK VIEIRA: Being a manager?

00:48:40.430 --> 00:48:42.500
AUDIENCE: Being a manager.

00:48:42.500 --> 00:48:45.950
So the talent to be a manager
